myFileMIB.name: myFileMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

myFileMIB.description: This module defines my file mibs.

myFileTransIndex.name: myFileTransIndex
myFileTransIndex.description: A value unique idenify the entry in the file transfer table. the index is assigned by agent random.

myFileTransMeans.name: myFileTransMeans
myFileTransMeans.description: The way to be used for any copy. Transport file by xmodem work in only in outband.other(3) mean transfer file by a way other than tftp(1) and xmodem(2)

myFileTransOperType.name: myFileTransOperType
myFileTransOperType.description: This object can be used for specifying the file transfer operation type, upload or download. using tftp service file transfer can implemente between the station and agent. in current agent,if synchronizing file,this object has no weight.

myFileTransSrcFileName.name: myFileTransSrcFileName
myFileTransSrcFileName.description: This object tell the tftp client to know the file name required to be received in tftp transfer mode;and send the file name list which separate with '\t' to synchronizing server.

myFileTransDescFileName.name: myFileTransDescFileName
myFileTransDescFileName.description: File name the file will save as. The object has no weight to file synchronizing.

myFileTransServerAddr.name: myFileTransServerAddr
myFileTransServerAddr.description: This object tell the address of transfer destination when required for file transmittion.

myFileTransResult.name: myFileTransResult
myFileTransResult.description: While the status of this entry is completed, this field of this entry is valid, and carry the operation result of file transfer.

myFileTransComplete.name: myFileTransComplete
myFileTransComplete.description: while the file transfer of use parameters stored by this entry is completed the value of this field will be true(1), and if not completed false(2).

myFileTransDataLength.name: myFileTransDataLength
myFileTransDataLength.description: the file length transferred, after the transfer is complete, this value is come to valid -- the valude of field myFileTransComplete is true(1).

myFileTransEntryStatus.name: myFileTransEntryStatus
myFileTransEntryStatus.description: entry status of this entry. and the means in this enviraments can reffer to the text-convention definition of the RowStatus.

myFileSystemMaxRoom.name: myFileSystemMaxRoom
myFileSystemMaxRoom.description: the max room of file system in units of MB.

myFileSystemAvailableRoom.name: myFileSystemAvailableRoom
myFileSystemAvailableRoom.description: the available room of file system in units of MB.

myFileMIBCompliance.name: myFileMIBCompliance
myFileMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the My File MIB

myFileMIBGroup.name: myFileMIBGroup
myFileMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing file ability to a My agent.

myFileTransMeansMIBGroup.name: myFileTransMeansMIBGroup
myFileTransMeansMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing myFileTransMeans to a My agent.
